#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus MCP Server: The First Java Server SDK to Support Streamable HTTP!"
msgstr "Quarkus MCP 服务器：首个支持可流 HTTP 的 Java 服务器 SDK！"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus MCP Server is blazing a trail as the first Java MCP server with "
"Streamable HTTP support—unlocking new possibilities for developers."
msgstr "Quarkus MCP 服务器是首款支持可流 HTTP 的 Java MCP 服务器，为开发人员带来了新的可能性。"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Model Context Protocol (MCP) is taking the developer world by storm, and "
"now, with its latest spec update: Streamable HTTP support has arrived!"
msgstr "模型上下文协议（MCP）正在开发者世界掀起一场风暴，现在，随着其最新规范的更新：可流 HTTP 支持已经到来！"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We're thrilled to announce that Quarkus MCP Server is the very first Java-"
"based MCP server SDK to embrace this innovation, making it easier than ever "
"for you to build, experiment, and deploy MCP-powered solutions—wherever you "
"need them."
msgstr ""
"我们非常高兴地宣布，Quarkus MCP 服务器是首个基于 Java 的 MCP 服务器 "
"SDK，它采用了这一创新技术，使您比以往任何时候都更容易构建、实验和部署 MCP 驱动的解决方案，无论您需要它们在哪里。"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-mcp-server/releases/tag/1.2.0[Quarkus "
"MCP Server 1.2] now supports Streamable HTTP alongside `stdio` and `SSE` "
"transports. This enables new possibilities for connecting your MCP servers "
"to mobile apps and cloud services. While the implementation is fully "
"functional, some advanced features like https://modelcontextprotocol.io/"
"specification/2025-03-26/basic/transports#resumability-and-"
"redelivery[Resumability and Redelivery] are planned for future releases."
msgstr ""
"link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-mcp-server/releases/tag/1.2."
"0[Quarkus MCP Server 1.2] 现在支持可流 HTTP 以及 `stdio` 和 `SSE` 传输。这为将 MCP "
"服务器连接到移动应用程序和云服务提供了新的可能性。虽然功能齐全，但一些高级功能（如 link:https://modelcontextprotocol."
"io/specification/2025-03-26/basic/transports#resumability-and-"
"redelivery[可恢复性和重新交付] ）计划在未来的版本中推出。"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why Streamable HTTP Matters"
msgstr "可流式 HTTP 为何重要"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Streamable HTTP is the approach MCP spec have taken for real-time, "
"efficient, and scalable communication between clients and servers. It opens "
"the door to new integrations and user experiences, especially for platforms "
"and devices where traditional transports like SSE or stdio aren't ideal."
msgstr ""
"流式 HTTP 是 MCP 规范为实现客户端与服务器之间实时、高效和可扩展的通信而采用的方法。它为新的集成和用户体验打开了大门，特别是对于 SSE 或 "
"stdio 等传统传输方式并不理想的平台和设备。"

#: _posts/2025-05-23-streamable-http-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And now, thanks to Quarkus MCP Server, Java developers are at the forefront "
"of this evolution. Whether you're building AI assistants, developer tools, "
"or next-gen chatbots, Streamable HTTP gives you the flexibility to reach "
"more users, faster."
msgstr ""
"现在，得益于 Quarkus MCP Server，Java "
"开发人员已经站在了这一演进的最前沿。无论你是在构建人工智能助手、开发者工具还是下一代聊天机器人，Streamable HTTP "
"都能让你灵活地、更快地接触到更多用户。"

